      "comment": "PAW PETROV (8) has a strong overall record having 19 wins and 31 places from 73 starts including a last start second (30.55) over 530m at this track. Has never been out of the money in eight starts this course and distance. Boxed wide but will go close with the right run. LIFE'S A BOUNTY (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (22.49) last time in a Grade 3/4/5 at Murray Bridge. Solid record here winning five races. One of the better chances. MAJESTIC MCLAREN (1) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only 2 lengths from Woodside Frankie in second (30.90) at this track. Expected to be in the finish again. PROCLIVITY (7) is worth including after a top-three finish most recently.",
